ologico Regionale Paolo Orsi","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/097",{"slug":128,"type":125,"name":124,"uri":126,"description":129,"location":130},"097","An outstanding collection of archaeological material. The collection ranges from Siracusa and the surrounding territory (Megara Hyblaia, Akrai, Kasmenai etc) to encompass all of eastern Sicily, reaching as far as Gela and Agrigento. The ground floor covers prehistory through to the end of the Classical period. Upstairs includes Hellenistic and Roman Syracuse and a display of material from the catacombs. A gallery displaying material from Hellenistic eastern Sicily is in preparation.",{"settlement":90,"region":90,"country":131,"address":132,"geo":133},"Italy","Viale Teocrito 66, 96100 - Siracusa",{"lat":134,"lon":135},37.07636989,15.2866213,{"_":137,"type":138},"279","inventory",{"_":140,"mainLang":141,"languages":142},"Latin","la",[140],{"type":144,"bibl":145},"edition",[146,160,19,171,181],{"type":147,"n":148,"author":149,"date":150,"citedRange":151,"ptr":155,"ref":156,"inscriptionDate":150,"title":157,"citation":158,"uri":159,"year":150},"corpus","CIL","Mommsen","1883",{"ref":152},{"_":153,"target":154},"7185","http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650770",{"target":156},"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI","Inscriptiones Bruttiorum Lucaniae Campaniae Siciliae Sardiniae Latinae. Pars posterior. Inscriptiones Siciliae et Sardiniae","\u003Cspan>T. Mommsen, \u003Ci>Inscriptiones Bruttiorum Lucaniae Campaniae Siciliae Sardiniae Latinae. Pars posterior. Inscriptiones Siciliae et Sardiniae\u003C/i>, Corpus Inscriptionum Latinarum, consilio et auctoritate Academiae Litterarum Regiae Borussicae editum, 10.2 (Berlin: G. Reimer, 1883)\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/GQN8UZSI",{"author":161,"date":162,"citedRange":163,"ptr":164,"ref":166,"inscriptionDate":162,"title":168,"citation":169,"uri":170,"year":162},"Ferrua","1989","no.361",{"target":165},"https://www.zo