">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[.]APRINAR[..]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000463_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-06-27\" src=\"ISic000463_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000463.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-06-27\" src=\"ISic000463-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000463_rear_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-06-27\" src=\"ISic000463_rear_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000463_rear.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2016-06-27\" src=\"ISic000463_rear-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text from autopsy\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan>Schubring: IORIAMA+; Mommsen: IORIAMAL\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"2\">2: \u003Cspan>Vertical stroke at start of line, but impossible to know if letter or decoration.\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Memorial of Maurus, seller of goat meat\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Transcribed by Schubring in materials sent to the Berlin academy in October 1865 (his no.219; now in the CIL archives), but no details of provenance are recorded. Ferrua proposed reading 'caprinarius' in the final line, accepted by both Rizzo and Chioffi.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Mommsen 1883 \u003Ca href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650770\" target=\"_blank\">7185\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1989 no.361 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rizzo 1989 100 no.96 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001640\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001640\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Chioffi 1999 88 no.114 \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Very well cut, tall, v-cut letters. A with a broken bar, M with vertical outers, short inner bars, N with short diagonal, O slightly ovoid.\u003C/p> Line 1  50-60  Line 3  65-68  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[251,254,257,260,263,266,269,272],{"id":252,"html":253},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: autopsy Prag 2016-06-27\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-